title: State Police in Cobleskill arrest Esperance woman for DWI (New York State Division of State ...
text: ( Source : New York State Division of State Police ) PRESS RELEASE October 10 , 2015-SP Cobleskill State Police in Cobleskill arrested an Esperance woman following a one car accident that occurred in the Town of Duanesburg on October 3, 2015 .
